    <section>
      <title>Changes in Edition 0.7</title>

      <para>The following changes were made:</para>

      <itemizedlist>
        <listitem>
          <para>The Maven build for Maven: The Definitive Guide was configured
          to use the <ulink
          url="http://github.com/tobrien/scribd-plugin/tree/master">Maven
          Scribd plugin</ulink>. To see the build configuration for this book
          see the <ulink
          url="http://github.com/sonatype/maven-guide-en/tree/master">maven-guide-en
          project</ulink> at GitHub. (<ulink
          url="https://issues.sonatype.org/browse/MVNDEF-128">MVNDEF-128</ulink>
          and <ulink
          url="https://issues.sonatype.org/browse/MVNDEF-127">MVNDEF-127</ulink>)</para>
        </listitem>

        <listitem>
          <para>Moved Ant, Ruby, and Groovy content to the Maven Cookbook.
          (<ulink
          url="https://issues.sonatype.org/browse/MVNDEF-118">MVNDEF-118</ulink>,
